Package clientSide.entities

Interface OrdinaryThiefCloning

All Known Implementing Classes:
AssaultPartyClientProxy, ConcentrationSiteClientProxy, ControlCollecSiteClientProxy, MuseumClientProxy
public interface OrdinaryThiefCloning
Ordinary Thief cloning. It specifies his own attributes. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
